data.description: ACCEPTING FHA LOAN ASSUMPTION!!!! 5.5%  Discover the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm in this stunning split-level home. With 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a seamless flow between living spaces, this residence offers a lifestyle of ease and elegance. The heart of the home is the newly renovated kitchen, a vision of contemporary style with sleek finishes, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. Upstairs, the master bedroom boasts an ensuite bathroom, while three additional bedrooms provide flexibility for your needs. All bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated for your convenience. The lower level offers a welcoming family room and a convenient half bathroom, making it the perfect space for relaxation and entertainment. Outside, a spacious backyard awaits your personal touch, and the property is nestled in a desirable neighborhood near schools, parks, shopping, and major transportation routes. Don't miss your chance to make this house your home – schedule a showing today and start living the dream!
